ing courtesy to those in a position to further their own interests.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#9999cc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub17.ezboard.com/usqualls77.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Squalls77</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#A0B0E0>(11/23/01 12:18:07 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub17.ezboard.com/fzenithsagepublic.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=157.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_lightbulb.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: made this clear ok?</span><hr size=1> hmm I think one cant camp things he cant kill...well i mean he can try camp it, and tell his guild to fast come to kill it when the mob spawn, but he cant claim it and not letting other people who are ready and have enough to kill it.  One good example is Lodizal.  When he spawned, he is almost down in less in 30 min or less.  who can claim he is camped? no one cus there are probably 5 or 6 people there will just claim they are camping it...so who gets?? the people who gather most quickly to slain him gets him.  Sorry but this is the way of life and eq, first come and first serve.  <br>Like Fear last time, clearly you guys dont have enough for it for another 2 or 3 hours, so why do we have to wait and waste our time for you guys to clear it so we can do CT.<br>The best way is for some of you who waited there for hours is to ask our officers nicely that if you could join our raid and maybe get some loot that we dont need, i am sure no zs need any pof armors, except loot from CT hehe<br>I am sure our officers will be just and will allow some of u to take some loots with u. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub17.ezboard.com/ugargo000.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gargo000</A></span><br> <span